			Researchwork
			
			Iaminterestedininvestigatingthepreparation,propertyandapplicationofnovelionicliquids(ILs).Themaininnovativeachievementsareasfollows:
1)AkindofsimpleammoniumILswithlowcost,easypreparation,andexcellentperformancewereprepared,andappliedinthecracking,hydrolyzing,andcondensingreactionasdualsolvent-catalyst.TheresultsshowedthatcatalyticactivitywassignificantlyinfluencedbytheacidityoftheseproticILs.TheindustrialapplicationofthesesimpleammoniumILswassuccessfulfortheproductionofcinnamicacid(1000t/y)and2-alkylpropene(1000t/y).Nationalawardfortechnologicalinvention2ndprize(inpublicity),Ministryofeducationscienceandtechnologyprogressaward2ndprize,andZhejiangprovincialscienceandtechnologyaward2ndprizewereawarded.
2)SomenovelsystemsforCO2andSO2capturebyILsweredeveloped.Forexample,akindofanion-functionalizedproticILsweredesignedandusedforCO2captureforthefirsttime.TheresultsshowedthatequimolarCO2capturecouldbeachievedduetothereactivityoftheanion,andtheabsorptionanddesorptionofCO2couldbeeasilytunedbythebasicityoftheseILs.

			
				
